Padre support for remote development mainly through SSH.

STATUS: ReDevel plugin is used in my daily work. It saves/sends
file (after Crtl+S keypress in Padre editor) to remote machine
through SSH. Plugin choose (based on actual editor's session name)
proper configuration with local to remote directories/files
mapping.

See files in docs directory for more info.

This package is provided with absolutely no warranty. As always,
you should conduct an appropriate level of testing before using
any new product in your production environment.
